docs/ROADMAP.md:39:   Execute locally or on VPS in a worktree, Docker/container, disposable workspace, or other bounded runtime.
docs/ROADMAP.md:55:The first practical value is one real end-to-end task run: the system accepts a meaningful task, plans it, decomposes it into 2-5 isolated subtasks, runs them in controlled environments, gathers artifacts, verifies the result, and returns an owner-ready report.
